Server switch:

Switch>en 
Switch#config t
Switch(config)#int fa0/1
Switch(config-if)#switchport mode trunk 
Switch(config-if)#exit 
Switch(config)#vtp mode server
Switch(config)#vtp domain ccna 
Switch(config)#vtp password 12
Switch(config)#exit 

Switch#show vlan 

Switch#en 
Switch#config t
Switch(config)#vlan 2
Switch(config-vlan)#name devi 
Switch(config-vlan)#exit 
Switch(config)#vlan 3
Switch(config-vlan)#name parasuraman 
Switch(config-vlan)#exit 
Switch(config)#vlan 4
Switch(config-vlan)#name livewire 
Switch(config-vlan)#exit 
Switch(config)#exit 

Switch#show vlan 

Transparent switch:

Switch>en 
Switch#config t
Switch(config)#int fa0/1
Switch(config-if)#switchport mode trunk 
Switch(config-if)#exit 
Switch(config)#int fa0/2
Switch(config-if)#switchport mode trunk 
Switch(config-if)#exit 

Switch(config)#vtp mode transparent 
Setting device to VTP TRANSPARENT mode.
Switch(config)#vtp domain ccna 
Switch(config)#vtp password 12
Setting device VLAN database password to 12
Switch(config)#exit 

Switch#show vlan 

Client switch:

Switch>en
Switch#config t
Switch(config)#int fa0/1
Switch(config-if)#switchport mode trunk 
Switch(config-if)#exit 
Switch(config)#vtp mode client 
Switch(config)#vtp domain ccna 
Domain name already set to ccna.
Switch(config)#vtp password 12
Setting device VLAN database password to 12
Switch(config)#exit 

Switch#show vlan 
